events.name: SUTD's Rustaceans (informal) meeting
events.description: Hi SUTD Rustaceans, Let's see who is interested in the Rust programming language and what is doing with it or why is willing to learn it.This is not strictly a technical meeting, please come ! Let's meet in front of the SUTD Auditorium (according to how many people will participate I'll try to book an adequate meeting room). http://rustaceans.org/
